CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 11, 1962, pg. 9 reads: "Mr. and Mrs. Charles Walker...married at St. James - Frances Clark, daughter of Mrs. Ethel Clark of Brushton, was married in St. James Roman Catholic Church July 21st, to Charles Walker, son of Mrs. Emma Walker, of San Mateo, Calif..."
TitMainTitle: Groom Charles Walker and Bride Frances Clark Walker, posed in back seat of car
